org.apache.polygene.test.serialization

Class AbstractPlainValueSerializationTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.polygene.test.AbstractPolygeneBaseTest
      • org.apache.polygene.test.AbstractPolygeneTest
        • org.apache.polygene.test.serialization.AbstractPlainValueSerializationTest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Assembler

    public abstract class AbstractPlainValueSerializationTest
extends AbstractPolygeneTest
    Assert that Serialization behaviour on plain values is correct. Implementations must:
    • implement Assembler.assemble(ModuleAssembly)
    • apply test SerializationSettings using withTestSettings(SerializationSettings) in assemble()
    • implement getSingleStringRawState(String)
